{"type":"section","nativeType":"section","number":"4566","heading":"Prohibition on purchase of United States defense contractors by entities controlled by foreign governments","label":"4566 Prohibition on purchase of United States defense contractors by entities controlled by foreign governments","identifier":"/us/usc/t50/s4566","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t50/ch55/schIII","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft50%2Fs4566","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":["Editorial Notes","CodificationSection was formerly classified to section 2170a of the former Appendix to this title prior to editorial reclassification and renumbering as this section.Section was enacted as part of the National Defense Authorization Act for Fiscal Year 1993, and not as part of the Defense Production Act of 1950 which comprises this chapter."],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"a","heading":"In general","label":"a In general","identifier":"/us/usc/t50/s4566/a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t50/s4566","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft50%2Fs4566%2Fa","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t50/s4566/a/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t50/s4566/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft50%2Fs4566%2Fa%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"is performing a Department of Defense contract, or a Department of Energy contract under a national security program, that cannot be performed satisfactorily unless that company is given access to information in a proscribed category of information; or","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t50/s4566/a/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t50/s4566/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft50%2Fs4566%2Fa%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t50/s4566/a/2/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t50/s4566/a/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft50%2Fs4566%2Fa%2F2%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"Department of Defense prime contracts in an aggregate amount in excess of $500,000,000; or","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t50/s4566/a/2/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t50/s4566/a/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft50%2Fs4566%2Fa%2F2%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"Department of Energy prime contracts under national security programs in an aggregate amount in excess of $500,000,000.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"b","heading":"Inapplicability to certain cases","label":"b Inapplicability to certain cases","identifier":"/us/usc/t50/s4566/b","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t50/s4566","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft50%2Fs4566%2Fb","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The limitation in subsection (a) shall not apply if a merger, acquisition, or takeover is not suspended or prohibited pursuant to .section 4565 of this title","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"c","heading":"Definitions","label":"c Definitions","identifier":"/us/usc/t50/s4566/c","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t50/s4566","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft50%2Fs4566%2Fc","